{
  "stem": "25178.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A little tiny village, it's a beautiful little city with woods.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was being-- he was being protected there because it was a preventorium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was-- what I understand, there was one thing that the Germans were afraid of, and that was to catch tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well this was to prevent it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they never bothered to, to come in and check.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this was kind of a safe heaven, or haven.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was another Jewish boy there who was hiding there as well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somehow [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] somebody found out that my brother was hiding there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And they told him-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] this all-- and they thought it was maybe better that he should leave the preventorium.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they didn't want to put me and the other boy in jeopardy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they hid him in their house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the-- the man who ran the place, in his house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And sometime later after that, my brother got another letter in the mail to report immediately [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to a forced labor camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But somehow-- I don't know exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I think he escaped or something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because he was able to survive in Germany without being in a camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He doesn't like to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
